apex-terminal (0.1.0) kali-dev; urgency=medium

  * Initial release for Kali Linux
  * GPU-accelerated terminal renderer (wgpu/WebGPU)
  * Native terminal multiplexer (client-server architecture)
  * AI middleware with MCP protocol + local LLM inference
  * C2 framework connectors: Sliver, Havoc, Mythic, Empire
  * Shell stabilization engine derived from pwncat
  * Lua-based configuration engine with Starship prompt integration

 -- Apex Terminal Team <dev@apex-terminal.io>  Sat, 16 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
